" mappings
map <C-[> <ESC>

map <C-u> scrollPageUp
map <C-d> scrollPageDown
map <C-b> scrollFullPageUp
map <C-f> scrollFullPageDown

" Navigation
map d closeTab
map u lastClosedTab
map <C-h> previousTab
map <C-l> nextTab
map ga firstTab
map ge lastTab
map R reloadTabUncached
map gu goUpUrl
map \ goToRootUrl
map <C-g> :execute vyP<CR>

